ScrollList_SetColumnProperties
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<TextGadgets=>textgadgets/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<scrolllist_set_column_properties>
Syntax:	ScrollList_SetColumnProperties
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = <flags=>scrolllist_set_column_properties_flags>
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x401a + 20 (16430)
r3 = gadget id
r4 = number of columns
r5 = pointer to data
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved.
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method sets properties for columns in the scroll list (requires TextGadgets 0.54). Currently only property 0 (column widths) can be altered.
